OL,3,CMan, 80, jailed for sex offences
OL,4,Cagainst children
OL,6,FA man from Coventry has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor eight years after being convicted
OL,8,Fof sexual abuse against two girls.
OL,10,FDavid Iles, 80, had pleaded not guilty
OL,11,Fto multiple sexual offences against
OL,12,Fchildren with one incident dating back
OL,13,Fmore than thirty years.
OL,15,FHis crimes were uncovered when one of
OL,16,Fthe girls reported to a family member
OL,17,Fshe had been abused by Iles between
OL,18,FJanuary 2022 and August 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
