PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774033868
OL,3,CMan, 80, jailed for sex offences
OL,4,Cagainst children
OL,6,FA West Midlands Police investigation
OL,7,Fbegan with officers also being told
OL,8,Fabout another woman who had been
OL,9,Fabused by him in 1994.
OL,11,FAn investigation found the woman, who
OL,12,Fwas a child at the time, had been
OL,13,Fabused by Iles between October 1994
OL,14,Fand October 1995.
OL,16,FIles appeared at Warwick Crown Court
OL,17,Fon 13 March after being found guilty
OL,18,Fof sexual assault on a girl under 13,
OL,19,Finciting sexual activity on a girl
OL,20,Funder 13 and indecent assault on a
OL,21,Fgirl under 16.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774033868
OL,3,CMan, 80, jailed for sex offences
OL,4,Cagainst children
OL,6,FHe was jailed for eight years and will
OL,7,Fserve four years on extended licence,
OL,8,Fand was also ordered to abide by a
OL,9,FSexual Harm Prevention Order
OL,10,Findefinitely.
OL,12,FDetective Constable Ruth Russell said:
OL,13,F"We take every single report of abuse
OL,14,Fextremely seriously whether it
OL,15,Fhappened yesterday or decades ago.
OL,17,F"Because of the woman and girl's
OL,18,Fbravery in this case we have been able
OL,19,Fto put Iles behind bars for his crimes
OL,20,Fand protected other children.
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
