CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774033868
OL,3,CMan, 80, jailed for sex offences
OL,4,Cagainst children
OL,6,F"I want to thank them for their
OL,7,Fcourage and strength in coming forward
OL,8,Fand working with us throughout this
OL,9,Fwhole process.
OL,11,F"I hope this shows other survivors
OL,12,Fthat we will always do all we can to
OL,13,Finvestigate and get justice for anyone
OL,14,Fwho reports sexual offences to us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@cO]
